  "doc_id": "19034",
  "text": "Based on medical ontologies e.g. UMLS [CITATION_1] , GO [CITATION_2] and GALEN [CITATION_3] HeC is investigating the mapping heuristics for integrated case data. It is evaluating the relative quality of several of these mapping discovery methods for integrated case data. As a consequence it is in the process of providing an optimal combination of the best methods with respect to the accuracy and computation times.",
